          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5: Foaling Management -->
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Foaling Management</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Eleven months is a long time. A lot can go wrong—or right—between breeding and birth. BreederHQ guides you through pregnancy with milestone tracking so nothing falls through the cracks.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Auto-Generated Pregnancy Milestones</h3>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="bg-[hsl(24,95%,53%)] text-white font-bold rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center mr-4 flex-shrink-0">15</div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold">Day 15 — Pregnancy Check</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600">First ultrasound to confirm pregnancy and check for twins</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start">
