    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Competition & Racing Records</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Show ring. Race track. Performance arena. BreederHQ tracks achievements wherever your horses compete.
      </p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
